1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 23=

21
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,480
Your Majesty.

22
00:01:28,590 --> 00:01:31,200
I made this calming soup myself.

23
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:34,150
I heard you can't sleep well lately.

24
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:36,350
This soup soothes the nerves best.

25
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:38,400
It will help you sleep well.

26
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,560
You're the only one

27
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,870
who truly cares for me.

28
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,150
Please have a taste.

29
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,000
Is it good?

30
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,950
Yes.

31
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,680
I heard

32
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,920
there's a war in the southwest.

33
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:55,710
Your Majesty,

34
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,150
you plan to send the 14th Prince to war.

35
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,400
You're worried about him?

36
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,510
I feel uneasy.

37
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,950
A real man

38
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:07,790
should achieve great things.

39
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:11,120
Besides, he won't go alone.

40
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:13,000
Many soldiers will protect him.

41
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,840
What I fear

42
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,800
isn't the danger of war.

43
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,520
Then tell me.

44
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,000
I know an old story,

45
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:23,710
and I'd like to tell you.

46
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,000
Go on.

47
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:31,120
In the Zhou Dynasty, there was a duke.

48
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,710
He's Duke Zhuang of Zheng.

49
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,360
His mother, Lady Jiang,

50
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,310
favored the younger son, Gong Shuduan.

51
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,280
And treated Duke Zhuang of Zheng
with cold disregard.

52
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,560
She even schemed to

53
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:42,280
replace him with his brother.

54
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,190
Duke Zhuang seemed to endure it,

55
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,960
but secretly laid a trap.

56
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,910
In the end, he killed his brother.

57
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:51,680
And he also confined his mother,
Lady Jiang,

58
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,630
on a raised platform for over a decade.

59
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,800
People only blamed the family feud

60
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,120
and the broken mother-son bond.

61
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,400
Yet the root of this calamity

62
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:03,120
was favoritism
and interfering in politics.

63
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,960
You compare me

64
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,680
to Lady Jiang?

65
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,190
Your Majesty.

66
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,520
If you care for the 14th Prince,

67
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,750
you should keep him away

68
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:18,750
from court politics.

69
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:21,030
Not push him into this mess.

70
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:21,870
How dare you!

71
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,800
You dare speak wildly of court affairs!

72
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,200
Guards!

73
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,310
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

74
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,750
Every word I say is sincere.

75
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,150
I beg you to see clearly
and judge fairly.

76
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,360
Ruizhu.

77
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:39,470
Take her to the sutra hall
to copy sutras.

78
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,150
Let her reflect on herself.

79
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,400
Your Majesty.

80
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:43,750
Your Majesty!

81
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:45,430
Your Majesty.

82
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,470
Your Majesty!

83
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:09,800
Greetings, Mother.

84
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,470
Rise.

85
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,710
Mother, Ye Jin meant no offense.

86
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,310
Please forgive her.

87
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,600
She didn't do it by accident.

88
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,480
She has far too many thoughts.

89
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,960
Mother.

90
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:24,870
If you still wish to see her again,

91
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,800
then stop pleading for her.

92
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,360
That girl's recklessness
needs to be corrected.

93
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:32,390
Otherwise, with her rashness,

94
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,270
I won't feel comfortable

95
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:36,000
having her serve by your side.

96
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,190
Lady Xiao's fate can be changed.

97
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,190
So can the 14th Prince's.

98
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,190
But how can I

99
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:52,950
stop him from going to the southwest?

100
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,390
Your Highness.

101
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,350
Ye Jin.

102
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:03,070
What did you say to the Empress Dowager?

103
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,720
Why is she so angry?

104
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:08,920
I only told her
the story of Duke Zhuang of Zheng.

105
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,440
You...

106
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,040
Why?

107
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,600
Because I saw your fate.

108
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,920
Listen to me, Your Highness.

109
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,230
Ye Jin.

110
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,750
If you go to the southwest,

111
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,040
you will die.

112
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,000
Ye Jin.

113
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,000
Ye Jin, sit.

114
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,230
Sit down.

115
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:48,870
So

116
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:52,310
that dream was a warning.

117
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,320
Ye Jin.

118
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:55,920
Are you alright?

119
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,560
General Gui has reached the southwest.

120
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,360
He grew up there.

121
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:06,310
So he knows the land and customs well.

122
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:08,040
The Yunnan soldiers he leads

123
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,680
are good at mountain warfare.

124
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:12,120
We think we will win this war.

125
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,750
Since I chose him,

126
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,390
I naturally trust his abilities.

127
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,390
Your Majesty is wise.

128
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,750
The Lan father and son are ridiculous.

129
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:20,190
They even pressured you in court

130
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:22,000
and tried to make you give in.

131
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:24,750
They never knew
Your Majesty already had a plan.

132
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,270
When the truth comes out,

133
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:28,040
the southwest will be peaceful.

134
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:30,430
The Lan father and son
have been arrogant for years.

135
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,390
And seized too much power.

136
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,160
They only did it because I was young.

137
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,860
This time,

138
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,160
I will make them know

139
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,190
their good days

140
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,920
are over.

141
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:41,800
The meeting is over.

142
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:42,920
You may leave.

143
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,160
We take our leave.

144
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,320
They...

145
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,190
What's wrong?

146
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:01,750
Your Highness, the Empress Dowager
had a heart attack last night.

147
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,040
The Imperial Physician said

148
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,510
she should move to
a quiet place to recover.

149
00:07:05,870 --> 00:07:06,950
So early this morning,

150
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,120
Cining Palace has been busy.

151
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,830
Ruizhu.

152
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:23,920
The Empress Dowager is awake.

153
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:26,190
Bring the warm medicine quickly.

154
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,720
Your Majesty.

155
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,510
How do you feel now?

156
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,310
The Imperial Physician said,

157
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:32,390
when you wake up,

158
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,390
you must take this medicine first.

159
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,040
What medicine is there to drink?

160
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:45,430
I'm in someone's way.

161
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,680
Some people want me

162
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,360
to die soon.

163
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:56,120
Don't think like that, Your Majesty.

164
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,390
When you were unconscious,

165
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,000
His Majesty was very worried.

166
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,480
He stayed by your side all the time.

167
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,390
But an urgent report came

168
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,720
and the war situation is serious,

169
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,040
so he went to court.

170
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:06,600
The 14th Prince is very ill.

171
00:08:06,620 --> 00:08:07,750
When he heard you were unconscious,

172
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,240
he insisted on
coming to take care of you.

173
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,720
We finally persuaded him to stay.

174
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,950
Putting on such a show

175
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:17,070
is only for others to see.

176
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,630
They are all ungrateful.

177
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,390
Ruizhu.

178
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,830
All my life,
I've been scheming for nothing

179
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:30,560
but these two sons.

180
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,120
But both of them

181
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,270
don't appreciate me.

182
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:39,510
Tell me, am I wrong?

183
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:41,360
You are a loving mother.

184
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:42,550
You could never be wrong.

185
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,510
I'm from the steppe.

186
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,670
On the steppe, we have an old saying.

187
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,200
"A young eagle flies high

188
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,840
only after facing storms alone."

189
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:54,150
You should be proud of His Majesty.

190
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:55,910
Only when he can
bear the weight of the realm

191
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,750
has he truly grown up.

192
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,390
Your Highness.

193
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:56,720
You...

194
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,200
Are you alright?

195
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,270
I slept so...

196
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,720
So tired.

197
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,670
My body feels broken.

198
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,920
Ye Jin.

199
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,080
Promise me.

200
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,240
Stay by my side forever.

201
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:19,110
Alright?

202
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,870
I'll ask mother for a marriage decree.

203
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:27,870
I want you to be my consort.

204
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:28,960
My only consort.

205
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,720
And then,

206
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,480
we'll leave the court.

207
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,000
Away from all troubles.

208
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:39,750
We'll be

209
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,840
a carefree couple.

210
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,440
Alright?

211
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,390
I'm sorry, Your Highness.

212
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,270
I can't marry you.

213
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,080
I can't leave the palace with you.

214
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,280
Why?

215
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:01,240
Because...

216
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,750
Because I have to stay with Zhi Hui.

217
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:07,870
Only when she becomes Empress

218
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,480
can I go back.

219
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:11,150
I'm not Ye Jin.

220
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,870
I don't belong here.

221
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,120
I don't belong to this palace.

222
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,200
I don't belong to this city.

223
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,870
I don't even belong to this era.

224
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,510
You're saying

225
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,870
things I can't understand again.

226
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:26,750
Your Highness.

227
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,910
Your Highness, I care for you.

228
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,960
But...

229
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,440
But I don't belong to this world.

230
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,720
I have to go back in the end.

231
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,510
I'm sorry.

232
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,910
I don't understand what you mean.

233
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,870
But as long as you are here,

234
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,670
I'll stay by your side.

235
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,510
I'll protect you.

236
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,270
And I'll never let you be hurt.

237
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,910
Even if you have another way home.

238
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:08,240
♪I am but an outsider♪

239
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:10,440
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

240
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:14,720
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

241
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:18,960
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

242
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:26,480
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

243
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:30,040
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

244
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:32,560
♪I know how this story ends♪

245
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:37,120
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

246
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:41,560
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

247
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:49,840
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

248
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:53,120
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

249
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:56,400
♪A history that no one can search♪

250
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,920
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

251
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,720
♪I am but an outsider♪

252
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,960
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

253
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:08,000
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

254
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:12,680
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

255
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:20,000
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

256
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:23,360
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

257
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,840
♪I know how this story ends♪

258
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:30,000
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

259
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:33,280
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

260
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:37,080
♪Please forget me and move on♪

261
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:43,320
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

262
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:54,840
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

263
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:08,120
♪When do I finally wake♪
